cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the development of a convolutional neural network for the automatic assessment of focus quality in whole slide images, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also evaluates the impact of focus quality on the accuracy of an AI cancer detection algorithm, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of deep learning techniques for image analysis and the development of a convolutional neural network also falls under deep learning (cs.DL) and multimedia (cs.MM).
